&gt;&gt; Is this thing working?

00:09:30.620 --> 00:09:31.620
&gt;&gt; Oh good.

00:09:32.620 --> 00:09:33.983
Okay. Well, Isabel Allende is
obviously very well known to you.

00:09:35.390 --> 00:09:35.523
And she has been beloved to you.

00:09:37.390 --> 00:09:41.523
She's been translated into 30
languages, sold 60 million copies

00:09:43.420 --> 00:09:45.420
of her books around the world.

00:09:45.420 --> 00:09:46.306
&gt;&gt; Where is the money?

00:09:46.000 --> 00:09:47.000


00:09:47.730 --> 00:09:48.730
[ Laughter ]

00:09:50.040 --> 00:09:50.133
&gt;&gt; She is read everywhere
from Rio de Janeiro to Tokyo

00:09:53.480 --> 00:09:57.413
and what people don't know is
what you are going to discover

00:09:58.030 --> 00:09:58.106
as I've discovered over these
15 years of knowing Isabel is

00:10:01.820 --> 00:10:05.553
that she is apart from being
this unbelievable work horse

00:10:05.790 --> 00:10:10.190
who works 10 hours a day and gets
