&gt;&gt; Now don't go anywhere
because we are

00:47:52.410 --> 00:47:57.010
about to confer the National Book
Festival Creative Achievement Award.

00:47:57.450 --> 00:47:57.603
I'd like to introduce Deanna
Marcum who is the Library

00:48:00.830 --> 00:48:01.823
of Congress' Associate
Librarian for Library Services.

00:48:03.370 --> 00:48:04.370
Deanna.

00:48:05.370 --> 00:48:06.740
&gt;&gt; Thank you.

00:48:05.000 --> 00:48:06.000


00:48:07.870 --> 00:48:08.870
[ Applause ]

00:48:11.500 --> 00:48:13.166
&gt;&gt; Good morning everyone.

00:48:13.530 --> 00:48:13.706
Isabel, that was absolutely
wonderful thank you

00:48:16.420 --> 00:48:19.153
so much it is my great
pleasure to present

00:48:20.430 --> 00:48:22.363
to Isabel Allende the Library

00:48:23.570 --> 00:48:27.636
of Congress National Book Festival
Creative Achievement Award.

00:48:28.500 --> 00:48:31.433
Ms. Allende for your
outstanding contribution

00:48:31.640 --> 00:48:35.706
to international letters, for
your involvement in the creation

00:48:35.880 --> 00:48:40.480
