your focus on the struggles of women

00:48:42.260 --> 00:48:46.193
and for your plays and children
stories a worldwide audience

00:48:47.280 --> 00:48:48.280
has risen.

00:48:49.280 --> 00:48:53.546
Ladies and gentlemen please join
me in recognizing Isabel Allende

00:48:54.930 --> 00:48:55.360
as the recipient of the
National Book Festival Creative

00:48:58.100 --> 00:48:59.300
Achievement Award.

